  <!-- EN: QBA-131R shotgun -->
  <CMC_QBAfournine.label>QBA-131R 霰弹枪</CMC_QBAfournine.label>
  <!-- EN: The QBA-131R utilizes twin-barrel magnetic rail acceleration technology to propel four fragmenting tungsten alloy penetrators at hyper-velocities. It possesses devastating piercing capabilities against projectile interceptors and composite armor. The trade-offs are its tremendous recoil and an archaic mechanical reloading system that compromises sustained fire rates. -->
  <CMC_QBAfournine.description>QBA-131R 采用双管磁轨加速技术，能将分裂式的四枚钨合金穿甲弹加速至极高初速，对现有的力场护盾及复合装甲具有毁灭性的贯穿力。代价是其惊人的后坐力，且老式的机械装填结构导致火力持续性较差。</CMC_QBAfournine.description>
